===== How to make the test grid =====

To calibrate the light-sheet, a broken-up test slide such as [http://www.edmundoptics.com/testing-targets/test-targets/resolution-test-targets/opal-glass-ronchi-ruling-slides/2838 this one] can be used. Typically, you would glue it to a sample holder (for which we use a Braun Omnifix-F 1 ml syringe):

